494
00:22:57,651 --> 00:23:01,222
Don't cry 'cause
you're so right.

495
00:23:01,255 --> 00:23:02,056
Don't try--

496
00:23:05,861 --> 00:23:07,363
NARUTO (VOICEOVER):
What's up with this?

497
00:23:07,396 --> 00:23:10,099
All we're doing are these
boring training missions.

498
00:23:10,133 --> 00:23:12,502
Then finally, we get a
chance at something big,

499
00:23:12,536 --> 00:23:14,940
and it turns out it's just
guarding this old man.

500
00:23:14,973 --> 00:23:18,310
And he says, I'm only a
kid, and calls me a loser.

501
00:23:18,344 --> 00:23:20,212
I won't tell you what
I called him back.

502
00:23:20,246 --> 00:23:23,049
But I did tell him, look,
someday I'll be-- hey,

503
00:23:23,082 --> 00:23:24,685
are you listening to me?

504
00:23:24,718 --> 00:23:26,979
Next time, "A
Dangerous Mission--

505
00:23:27,012 --> 00:23:28,812
Journey to the Land of Waves."

506
00:23:28,846 --> 00:23:32,028
Don't miss me as
a full-on ninja!

